title: Legacy
description: Estranged brothers reunite at a small airport to try to find their recently deceased father's hidden fortune.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Around the World in Eighty Years
description: When Helen has another audition and is not chosen; Brian points out that she dresses too conservatively and that she should consider sexing it up a little. Fay is attracted to a man who has been traveling around the world and is on the last leg of his journey. When Fay asks him why doesn't he complete it, he claims that if he does he will die.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Return to Nantucket: Part 1
description: A pilot who knows Brian has a layover at Nantucket and tells him that his ex is moving to London. Brian learns that she'll have a layover in Boston so sends her a message asking her to meet him. When Joe learns of this he tells Brian she won't be there. But Brian decides to go even with a fog covering the island. Joe and Helen decide to follow him.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Return to Nantucket: Part 2
description: Brina's ex shows up and he convinces her to go back to Nantucket with him. Helen is upset that she doesn't remember her. Later when she and Joe are alone she comes on to him.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: There Once Was a Girl from Nantucket
description: Brian asks a girl out and she agrees on the condition that he find someone for her friend Cindy. And he volunteers Joe. Joe initially refuses but Brian guilts him into it. Later he learns that Cindy is very "popular", which makes him reconsider, but then Helen guilts him. And at their date one of her exes shows up and when he treats her crudely Joe stands up for her.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: All for One and Two for Helen
description: Joe suspects the worst when Brian and Helen spend an evening alone together.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Puppet Master
description: Trying to get Helen to change her policy about dating pilots, Brian hires an actor to pretend to be a pilot but who shares the same interests that Helen has. It isn't long before they're dating. But things go awry when the guy really falls for Helen and she makes some decisions that will greatly affect her life.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Story of Joe
description: A reporter comes to Nantucket to do a story on Joe. But when he talks to Brian and hears some of his stories, he decides to interview him. And Joe is upset.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: A Little Nightmare Music
description: When a conductor comes to the island, Helen tries to talk to the man and maybe play for him but she freezes. Brian comes up with the plan to hold to one of his baggage. Helen then goes to where he is staying to return it and play for him. And he tells her that she's no good. That's when Joe goes to see the man and tell him off.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Sports and Leisure
description: Roy invites himself into the group's social circle.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: A Standup Kind of Guy
description: A guy calls Joe, telling him they were close years ago. But Joe doesn't remember him. But when Joe meets him and asks him to be his best man at his wedding Joe can't refuse. Things get weird with the wedding approaching.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: It's Not the Thought, It's the Gift That Counts
description: Joe and Brian compete to see who get Helen the better birthday gift as a means to try and impress her.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Hell Hath No Fury Like a Police Woman Scorned
description: After getting Joe out of many unpaid parking tickets by flirting with the police officer, but soon learns she isn't his type. Also, Lowell keeps a video camera handy in case something funny happens.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Friends or Lovers?
description: Due to desperation and loneliness, Joe and Helen decide to go on a date. To spare his feelings, they choose to keep it a secret from Brian.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: There's Always Room for Cello
description: Roy gets the surprise of his life when he agrees to let his star athlete son take cello lessons from Helen.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: A Terminal Christmas
description: After everybody's holiday plans fall through, they decide to surprise Faye at her Christmas party. When they arrive, they discover she'd lied about her plans and find her all alone.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Airport '90
description: Helen decides to take flying lessons from Joe but his classes are too long and boring so Brian offers to let her fly the plane. Shortly after, Brian is injured and Helen finds herself behind the controls.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: My Brother's Back - And There's Gonna Be Trouble

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Looking for Love in All the Wrong Places

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Love Means Never Having to Say Geronimo

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Mother Wore Stripes
description: Joe and Brian's mother who left them, comes back. While Brian is happy to see her, Joe isn't. And things get worse when she tells them why she chose not to return.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Murder She Roast
description: Brian is forced to live with Faye for a week and jumps to conclusions when he thinks he sees her on a fugitive TV show.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Naked Truth
description: 10 months after moving to New York, Helen calls Joe to say hi. Joe doesn't tell her that he's been seeing someone else. Later he talks to everyone looking for someone to tell him that it's best not to tell Helen. But Brian tells him he has to. So they go to New York and they find her working in a strip club. Joe tries to tell her about his new girlfriend but she tells him that she's down on her luck. So he tells her to come back to Nantucket, without telling her. When they arrive she finds out unexpectedly.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Is That a Subpoena in Your Pocket...?
description: Following Helen's damage to his office, Joe tries to get her to pay for the damages. When she refuses, Joe decides to sue her.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Taming of the Shrew
description: Helen's anger issues with Joe result in her attending a group meeting after the persuasion of her friends.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: I Ain't Got No Bunny
description: Joe and Brian discover that Lowell is sleeping at the airfield. He tells them that he and his wife, Bunny are on the skids because he thinks that she's throwing herself at other men. They tell him to try and work things out. So he takes his wife out. The next day, he tells them things didn't work out because he assumed she was hitting on a guy. He then asks them if one of them can talk to her. Brian offers to do but Joe thinks he shouldn't. When he talks she comes on to him and Joe walks in before anything happens. Now they have to tell Lowell he has to get away from her.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: If Elected, I Will Not Live

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: My Brother's Keeper
description: A wealthy woman comes to the island and takes a liking to Brian and it isn't long before he becomes her boy toy. The gang is hoping that Brian can get her to invest with them or donate to some benefit they're involved with. But Joe tells Brian that he should be ashamed of himself but is having too much of a good time to listen. Joe then decides to tell her what he thinks of her but she cuts him off by saying she wants to invest with him, that's when he changes his tune.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Crate Expectations
description: It's Joe's birthday and he tells everyone that he prefer not to celebrate it. Brian decides to throw him a surprise party and everyone agrees to help. Later Joe overhears them planning the party and he's touched. But later they all realize they have prior commitments so they have to reschedule. Fay then tells Joe that he has to stay and take receipt of some items that are going to be delivered to the hanger later and that everyone else has plans. Joe thinking that it's a ruse to make sure he's around for the party goes along with it. But when a man delivering a crate arrives, he thinks that they're in the crate and is expecting them to be inside but is disappointed that they're not. And the next day is sore at everyone for pulling a fast one on him. So Brian tells him the party was rescheduled and asks him to be there. And when Joe tells Brian of the assumption he made about the crate, Brian decides to do that. But the person Brian puts in charge of bringing the crate to Joe makes a mistake.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Ladies Who Lunch
description: When Helen and Gail continue to bicker, Joe wants them to make peace. So he tells them to spend some time together and it isn't before long that they're buddies and talking about Joe's deepest secrets. When word comes out that the President will have a layover; Roy wants to get his picture taken with him and Fay wants to touch the First Lady which she has been doing with the last 8 First Ladies.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Try to Remember the Night He Dismembered

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Bogey Men
description: Brian tries to scam a time-share out of a weekend of golf by signing up for a sales pitch he has no intention of attending. Joe, Roy, and Lowell tag along. The trip is ruined by a tropical storm in Florida.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Marriage, Italian Style
description: Antonio learns that he's facing the possibility of being deported. They think the best way is for him to marry an American. So they try to find someone willing to marry him. But on the day that he told immigration that he's suppose to get married, the woman they found doesn't show up.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Divorce, American Style
description: Helen marries Antonio to keep him from being deported. But she's dreading having to stay married to him for the time required for him to get his citizenship. But Brian learns of another way for Antonio to get his green card. And that is for him to enter the Green Card lottery, so Helen tries to get as many applications out so that he can get his green card and she can no longer be married to him.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: This Old House
description: Brian and Joe learn that the house where they lived is going to be demolished. While Faye tries to see if she can do anything to keep it form happening, they go to see it one last time. And they remember when they first moved in and how things were when their parents were still together. And they even recall how they first met Helen.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Planes, Trains and Visiting Cranes
description: Frasier Crane comes to the island to conduct a workshop. And it's while conducting his workshop that Helen sees him and says he's the man who ruined her life. it seems that he advised her to leave the island and go to New York. Frasier brings her on stage to talk and while he fails to convince her, it was not his fault, he passes the buck to Joe. Who then stands up and says he did nothing.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Das Plane
description: Joe donates a free trip to a charity auction. And the man who bought is Carlton Blanchard, an old man is not quite all there. When asked where he wants to go, he answers Las Cruces, New Mexico which is not where they usually go. At first, they're not willing to do it but when he tells them, he's going to see his brother whom he hasn't seen in years, they give it a shot. Lowell and Antonio tag along.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Take My Life, Please
description: When Helen loses her job as a Realtor, she finds herself wondering what's she's going to do now. Antonio suggests she take a test that determines what job she would be suitable for. She takes it but when the results arrive, Antonio saw the results and tells everyone that it said her choices were either music or food service. The gang thinks they should change the results. So Joe tells Fay to put in law which is something Joe says she was interested in before. When Fay asks what should she put on the second choice, Joe tells her to put something. Helen reads and is more taken by the second choice, stand up comedian, so she tries to get her routine ready.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Four Dates That Will Live in Infamy
description: The gang goes on dates through a service and meet up at the Club Car to tell their odd stories.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Say It Ain't So, Joe
description: Joe's old baseball coach wants him to bring the player who's poised to break Joe's record. While on route, Joe learns that the player among other things will be getting a car and Joe will be the butt of some jokes. When the airport tells Joe that it's not uncertain if conditions are good for him to land but they want him to make that decision and he decides not to making people think he didn't want the player to break his record.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: As Fate Would Have It
description: The episode begins with everyone in a plane headed for Boston but they're caught in a storm and uncertain of their fate. Then we see how they got there; it began when Helen got an opportunity to perform in Boston. But everyone can't make it because prior engagements. Then somehow everyone becomes free.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Lifeboat
description: The gang who were on their way to watch Helen perform but something goes wrong with the plane and they land in the water. They're on a lifeboat in the middle of the ocean. And they wonder if someone will find them. But they are found. And when Joe goes back to the island, he considers leaving because without the plane, that's the end of Sandpiper.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

description: Lowell convinces Helen to go on a date.

Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

description: Helen dates a guy with an annoying laugh. Antonio has trouble with his jerk neighbor.

title: I Love Brian
description: Hoping to impress Alex, Brian claims to know Clint Black. So they go to Boston where he has a show and they go to his hotel room and that's when things get complicated.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Date Package Number Seven
description: Alex finally agrees to a date with Brian, only to find out later it was all a setup.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Stop in the Name of Love

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Business or Pleasure
description: Joe brings a guy to the island whom he hopes will invest in Sandpiper so that Joe can expand the business. But when the guy sees Helen, he asks Joe to fix them up. Joe asks Helen to go out with him and she reluctantly does. It's after that Joe realizes that he used Helen and tries to get her out of it but she's fallen for him.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Black Eye Affair
description: While trying to create a perfect evening with her boyfriend, Davis, Helen runs into obstacle after obstacle with various friends who assist in aiding with what can only be certain disaster.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Joe Blows: Part 1
description: Episode begins with what appears to be Joe's lifeless body floating in water and we hear his voice telling how he got to this point. It began when a passenger is looking for his briefcase that he left on the plane and was not returned to him. And he demands that Joe locate it. And that's when everyone starts dumping on Joe; Antonio wanting Joe to co-sign with him when he goes to the bank to apply for a loan to buy a new cab, Brian concerned that his first intimate moment with Alex was not out standing, Helen concerned about her relationship with her boyfriend, and Fay, who upon learning that one of her late husbands is being transferred to the same cemetery that another one of her husbands is buried at, asks Joe to keep it from happening. And Roy keeps on playing a radio commercial for his service on tape and Lowell is tinkering with a motorcycle that drives Joe mad. And when a reporter from the newspaper of Joe's alma mater comes to interview him, and when he brings up the fact that Joe didn't do the things he set out to do. Joe's about to snap.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Joe Blows: Part 2
description: With Joe still gone, everyone is wondering where he is and when will he return, especially Brian who's worried about the business. When Joe's credit card bill arrives, Brian learns he was last in Mustique. So he goes there to try and find him and does. But Joe doesn't want to go back cause he's still having fun. Brian reminds him that the business needs him. Joe then turns control to him. Brian returns and finds himself swamped. And his relationship with Alex suffers. And things get worse when the bank takes the plane.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Ready, Teddy, Go
description: Davis comes to the island and brings Helen out and invites Joe, Brian, and Alex to come along. They go back to his hotel room and while he goes to freshen up, Helen goes through his luggage and finds a present which she assumes is for her and sees it's something extremely personal. When he tells her that he has something for her, it's not what she saw. So she wonders if he's seeing someone else.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Oh Give Me a Home Where the Mathers Don't Roam
description: Joe and Brian are tired of Lowell, who has been staying with them since Brian sank his boat, bossing them around want him out of the house, so they try to get him to buy his own place. But when they find him staying at the airfield instead of his new place, they learn that Lowell has never been on his own before. But when Roy tells him a "story" about his "brother" whom he never saw after he "left", Lowell decides to give it a shot.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Boys Will Be Girls
description: Coach Mattay visits the island and resumes belittling Joe and Brian just like he did back when they were in high school. They decide to play a prank on him that gets way out of hand.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Whose Wife Is It Anyway?
description: After spending the night with Helen, Joe thinks they're a couple again. But she goes off to see her boyfriend who proposed to her. So Joe goes after her.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Twisted Sister
description: Helen's sister Casey arrives and spoils Joe's dinner plans with Helen.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Shrink
description: Brian's going to a psychiatrist to deal with his break up with Alex and is grown dependent on him. Joe and Helen see him and he makes a remark that makes them think they're not suitable for each other. And Lowell is looking for his hat.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Spark and How to Get It

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Is That a 10 Foot Sandwich or Are You Just Glad to See Me?

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Miss Jenkins
description: Miss Jenkins, the gang's former teacher returns to the island to teach. And the boys had a great crush on her. Brian asks her out and he takes her home and she spends the night. Joe and Helen learn she spent the night. Joe praises Brian till her learns what happened between them. And Roy learns that a guy is dating his mom and wonders why?

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: If It's Not One Thing, It's Your Mother
description: Helen's mom comes to the island and she's hoping she'll give her money to help with the wedding as she did with Casey. When she arrives, Casey who hasn't told her mom that her husband left her so she pretends that he is out of town. When she gives Helen the check she's shocked of how little it is. At the same time Brian and Lowell compete to see who can more of her food. And Antonio clings to her.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Wrong Stuff
description: Brian tells Joe they need to drum up more business, so to do that he suggests that they hire a celebrity spokesman and the man Brian wants him to consider is Ace Galvin, a former astronaut. Brian brings him over to the island and while trying to schmooze him, he goes around like a wild man which makes Joe wonder if he's the right man. But w3hen it comes time for him to sign, they learn that Roy snatched him. Roy spends his time gloating until he learns of his latest antic.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Have I Got a Couple for You

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Let's Call the Whole Thing Off

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Ex, Lies and Videotape
description: Brian is asked to appear on a talk show supposedly because he's s hunky guy and he asks everyone to go. And when the show starts he learns that he was tricked to go on the show because they're there to talk about guys who use women and dump them. Something he denies till the host reveals the other guest, Brian's ex Alex. And she goes on about how things were fine between them till they decided to make a commitment which he backed out of. After the show Alex goes to the island and hashes things out with Brian which ends with them hooking up. And now Brian wants to end it.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Portrait of the Con Artist as a Young Man
description: Casey discovers Lowell has artistic talents and tries to exploit him. Brian accidentally sends a picture of his penis to Helen's mom.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Love Life and Times of Joe and Helen

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Nuptials Off
description: With their wedding approaching, Joe tells Helen she's not doing her part like getting their marriage license. She goes to get it and learns that she and Antonio whom she married so that he wouldn't get deported are still married. It seems that someone forgot to submit the divorce papers and that someone is Helen. Now if she files now it will take a month or two for it to be processed and the wedding is a few weeks away. So she turns to Roy who advises her to go to Mexico to get a quickie divorce. She first tries to get Joe out of town so he doesn't find out. She needs Brian to fly her to Mexico. But Antonio first wants to get the marriage annulled. So she and Helen meet with the priest who tries to convince them to reconcile. But when the plane is damaged they try to get Lowell who sick to fix it. And when Joe's departure is delayed Helen tries to keep him from finding out that the airline is closed for the week end among other things.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Boys Just Wanna Have Fun
description: Brian throws Joe a bachelor party before his wedding to Helen. Helen thinks is's stupid but let's them do it. But Brian does a bad job at planning it that they end up in a rundown hotel room and the stripper he got is not attractive. While Casey throws Helen a celebration of her own with a male stripper.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Here It Is: The Big Wedding
description: It's Joe and Helen's wedding day. Brian and Casey are suppose to help them; Brian's suppose to get the tuxedos and Casey is suppose to help Helen get ready. But because they hooked up the night before, they get up late and scurry to get their tasks done. But Brian gets the wrong tuxedos and Casey is so stressed that she messes up Helen's make up. And when Brian gets the tuxedos, he runs into Casey and they do it again and he throws them into a laundry cart and they're taken away. And Antonio who was hoping to tell Casey how he feels about her, upon learning what happened between her and Brian attacks him and knocks the wedding ring into the toilet. Joe tries to get it but gets stuck.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Burnin' Down the House: Part 1
description: Brian & Casey accidentally burn down Joe's house. Helen and Joe spend their honeymoon making love.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Death Becomes Him
description: A member of a wealthy family hires Joe and Brian to go to Miami to pick up the remains of the family patriarch, who died there. But because they drank a lot the night before they left, Joe got the wrong casket. So now they try to get the right one but there's going to be a viewing so what are they to do. Brian decides to let Joe take the dead man's place till the body arrives. And while waiting he learns all sorts of things about the man and his family.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Person Formerly Known as Lowell
description: Lowell witness a crime. The perp then tries to get him not to testify. The Feds then offer to place him in the Witness Protection Program but when he learns that if he does, he will no longer be able to see his friends. So he asks Joe what he should do but Joe tries to give him advice but tells him ultimately it's his decision.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: She's Gotta Have It
description: When the insurance company gives Helen a big check for what she lost in the fire she goes on a shopping spree. Casey refuses to have sex with Brian unless they can find something they share in common. Antonio depressed at his (lack of a) love life decides to go back to his ex who is hideous.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: When a Man Loves a Donut

title: 'Twas the Heist Before Christmas
description: It's Christmas. Joe wants to bring Helen to Vermont but Helen wants to throw a traditional Christmas party. Joe agrees on the condition that as soon as it's over they go to Vermont. So Helen invites everyone and Brian tels Casey he's bringing a date because of what happened between them. She tells him she's also bringing a date; only it's lie. She she tries to find someone and picks Lewis. Things go bad when Joe learns that the road to Vermont will be closed in a few hours so he tries to rush the party. And when Antonio brings gifts for everyone but they don't, he gets irate. When everybody tries to leave Helen stops them and they discover their wallets are missing and they accuse each other.

title: Bye George
description: Lyle, a man Fay met while on vacation comes to the island to court her. He proposes to her and they were in the process of getting married when the minister utters his full name. That's when Fay freaks out, because he has the same name as her other dead husbands. She then goes to Joe who is nursing a cold to ask him what she should do.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Team Player
description: Joe and Brian decide to go to a hockey game in Boston. They ask Antonio to man the counter. He gives the last seat to an old woman. And then a guy who says he was booked to go o the flight arrives. But because he was late Antonio gave sway the last seat. He says that he will regret it. Joe and Brian return and say the game was disappointing because the star player wasn't there. And Antonio tells them about the guy and they learn it was the hockey player. He later goes on the air and blames Sandpiper for his missing the game. And that's when they're the most hated people on the planet.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Lynch Party
description: Helen learns that her ex boyfriend Davis has been detained in Asia for over a year and is now on his way back to see her. She then tells Joe to go to Boston to get something. The guys are wondering what's up with Helen. She tells them that she didn't break up with him when she accepted Joe's proposal. She tells them that on the night she was going to see Davis, Joe proposed to her and she accepted. She told Joe that she has to see him alone but when she sees him, he surprises her with a surprise engagement party. And before she could tell Davis she accepted Joe's proposal he left for Asia. When he arrives she finds it difficult to tell him that she married Joe. And when Joe comes back the guys keep him from seeing Helen with Davis.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: One Flew Over the Cooper's Nest
description: When Joe learns that Sandy Cooper, the woman he says is obsessed with him, is coming he freaks out. Helen thinks he's out of his mind. And when she arrives, she's there for Brian. Joe goes on of how demented she is, Helen takes him to a therapist. But during one of his sessions Sandy shows up claiming to be his wife.

title: The Lady Vanishes
description: After a chance encounter, Antonio searches for the girl he shared a moment with in the airport. He enlists everyone's help to try to find her. Brian and Helen size up women at the ticket counters for emotional baggage that they might carry.

title: The Lyin' King
description: Joe and Brian learn that a woman whom they know is an exotic dancer and will be performing for the last time so they decide to go. But Joe has to find a way not to tell Helen. But when she asks him where he is going, he makes up a story of volunteering at a retirement home. And in order to be able to look her in the eye he goes to the home.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Love Overboard
description: When Casey discovers where her wayward husband is, she goes after him to get back what re ran off with. Only when she finds him he claims he lost everything.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Porno for Pyros
description: Joe, Helen, Brian, and Casey are fed up with their living arrangements, and Joe's "big board"; however, Felix the Contractor says the sinkhole on Joe and Helen's plot isn't the only delay in building their new house. Joe shows Helen the house of their dreams; but what to do with their poured foundation? In the meantime, Antonio gets $1000 from his taxes and decides he is going to spend it all on himself. Unfortunately, a broken tooth leads to a series of unfortunate events that whittles his check down. It all ends in fire and chaos, reminiscent of... last year.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: ...Like a Neighbor Scorned
description: Brian and Casey burn down Helen's house, Joe and Helen burn down Brian's house. This is too much of a coincidence for the insurance company. Joe, Brian, Helen, and Casey must sweat it out with the insurance adjuster before Antonio shows her passion can ignite a flame.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Maybe It's You
description: Brian's vow to find deeper relationships is tested by beautiful but dumb Dani. Joe tries to deal with his best friend not inviting him to a wedding.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Too Beautiful for You
description: Antonio works a suicide hotline one night and finds himself on a date with a depressed caller. When she turns out to be gorgeous he wonders how long until he gets dumped. Helen has to compete with a sandwhich vendor cart.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: The Gift of Life
description: It's Halloween and everybody wants to enjoy it and go to parties. But a guy shows up and buys a ticket; Joe and Brian don't want to fly him cause they have plans. The guy gets a call from his wife who had earlier dumped him. He says that he's a medical courier and he is carrying the gift of life. But Joe and Brian convince him to go to his wife and he leaves his cooler behind. They look inside and see a canister that says Nelson's heart. They assume it's a heart for a transplant. So they try to find out where it goes.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Olive or Twist
description: Casey encourages Brian to use his insurance money to open a martini bar. Things go awry when the first customer through the door slips and falls. Brian's problems are compounded when he learns Casey never got insurance. Roy and Faye hunt for ET's.

title: Just Call Me Angel
description: Brian becomes a hero when he has to land a jumbo-jet while returning home from a trip to Las Vegas. He doesn't handle the resulting fame very well.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Fay There, Georgy Girl
description: When Fay sells the things of her dead husbands, they haunt her.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Escape from New York
description: Brian and Helen's trip to New York to see "Rent" turns into a nightmare when the theatre refuses to transfer the tickets from Helen's benefactor to her. A con-man robs them of their money, Helen is forced to compete in a drag queen contest. A bad back leaves Joe in the house alone with a talkative Antonio.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: House of Blues
description: Kicked out by Joe and Helen, Brian and Casey move into a new home with the help of a new roommate Antonio who actually lives with his girlfriend. Things suddenly become crowded when Antonio is dumped and has to move back home. Joe and Helen's nudism has them threatened with blackmail when the neighbor kids snap photos of them.

title: Dreamgirl
description: The brothers hire Shannon, a beautiful temp, to fill in for vacationing Fay. Brian is very attracted to her and has to keep running into Helen's freezer to keep from making a fool of himself.

title: Final Approach: Part 1
description: Joe makes a music room in the attic for Helen. He moves a piece of luggage out for Brian, who discovers a secret note from their deceased father and key for a lock box. The duo set out on another finders keepers quest just like they did eight years earlier. They enlist Faye, Antonio an Casey on their quest which takes them to Boston, New York, and eventually back to Nantucket, only to find another suitcase in the airport locker, right next to the one from 8 years before. Helen plays for another symphony and gets turned down again.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran

title: Final Approach: Part 2
description: This time the suitcase actually contains money - a lot of money. Brian and Joe fight over what to do with the money, Joe always practical, Brian always impulsive, and go their separate ways. This leaves Faye wondering if she will still have a job, but instead Joe offers her 5% of the company for her loyalty. Helen hears back from the conductor in her interview and is invited to study with him in Vienna, but Joe doesn't want to leave Sandpiper. But when he learns of Helen's amazing opportunity he makes the ultimate sacrifice and finally actually agrees to sell Sandpiper to Roy, to go with her to Vienna. Brian readies for his departure to Bali, with Casey clinging at his heels, and readily signs for the sale, but after Joe signs Brian comes back and rips the contract. He tells Joe he will run Sandpiper for one year, and then Joe has to come back. This is of course much to the dismay of Casey, who has told off everyone on the island and quit her job. Joe and Helen leave, and Sandpiper goes on. But sadly not Wings.

roles.char: Fay Evelyn Schlob Dumbly DeVay Cochran
